cranelift) for common Cranelift/LLVM builder APIs\r\n  * [#55627] ~~common tools used by SSA backends could be placed in `rustc_codegen_ssa`~~\r\n  * refactor `rustc_codegen_ssa` APIs to match Cranelift, leave LLVM second-class\r\n    * unaddressed comments from #55627 may be relevant here\r\n* split the metadata, \"optimize + generate machine code\" (should it be called \"`binemit`\"?) and linking components, out of `rustc_codegen_ssa`", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/45274/reactions", "total_count": 8, "+1": 7, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 1, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/45274/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}